description: Returns a list of the Amazon CloudWatch RUM app monitors in the account.

nested_items.name: AppMonitorSummaries
nested_items.description: An array of structures that contain information about the returned app monitors.

nested_items.name: Created
nested_items.description: The date and time that the app monitor was created.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The unique ID of this app monitor.

nested_items.name: LastModified
nested_items.description: The date and time of the most recent changes to this app monitor's configuration.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of this app monitor.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: The current state of this app monitor.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token that you can use in a subsequent operation to retrieve the next set of results.
